content: I am a research assistant in the Digital Life-cycle Management Group at WMG, University of the Warwick. I have submitted my doctoral dissertation and am awaiting my viva. My doctoral research focused on utilising the spatial and spatio-temporal correlations in a manufacturing assembly process to improve the quality of the product during the early design phase.
